          p Only Natural Pet EasyDefense Flea & Tick Wipes protect your pet naturally. These biodegradable towelettes are made with FSC certified material, infused with geraniol and peppermint oil, and are a safe and convenient way to naturally repel fleas and ticks.
          
          td
          tr

      section
        table.table#notesTable
          tr
            img(src='/crate.png' style='width:25%' onclick='onClick(this)' alt='Great Choice® Double Door Wire Dog Crate')
            button.btn(type="button" v-on:click="addNote" style='background-color:orange') BUY
            tr  ₱ 6181.29
          p
            | Great Choice® Double Door Wire Dog Crate
          p
