          p The Great Choice Double Door Dog Crate provides training and containment solutions for the largest of breeds. The crate features convenient front and side door access, a heavy-duty corner drop-pin design, and slide-bolt latches that keep your pet safe and secure. The tough, ABS plastic pan is easy to clean and the black electro-coat finish provides long lasting protection. Only at nUB. 
     
          td
          tr
      
      section
        table.table#notesTable
          tr
            img(src='/treat.png' style='width:25%' onclick='onClick(this)' alt='Purina® Beggin Strips Dog Treat - Bacon')
            button.btn(type="button" v-on:click="addNote" style='background-color:orange') BUY
            tr  ₱ 225.23
          p
            | Purina® Beggin Strips Dog Treat - Bacon
          p
          b DESCRIPTION:
          p As the original strip that started it all, Purina Beggin' Strips Bacon Flavor adult dog snacks offer your best buddy an over-the-top bacon experience. Made with real bacon, these treats actually smell and taste like everyone's favorite sizzlin' breakfast fare. 
     
          td
          tr

      section
        table.table#notesTable
          tr
            img(src='/bowl.png' style='width:25%' onclick='onClick(this)' alt='Top Paw® Halloween Spider Web Dog Bowl')
            button.btn(type="button" v-on:click="addNote" style='background-color:orange') BUY
            tr  ₱ 240.28
          p
            | Top Paw® Halloween Spider Web Dog Bowl
          p
          b DESCRIPTION:
          p Feed your dog in a bowl that allows him to join in on the Halloween fun with this Top Paw Halloween Bowl. This fun bowl features spider webs along its outside with a scary spider inside, and includes a non-skid bottom so that it will stay in place. Only at nUB. 
     
          td
          tr

      section
        table.table#notesTable
          tr
            img(src='/food.png' style='width:25%' onclick='onClick(this)' alt='Purina® Pro Plan® Savor Shredded Blend Adult Dog Food - Chicken & Rice')
            button.btn(type="button" v-on:click="addNote" style='background-color:orange') BUY
            tr  ₱ 2460.90
          p
            | Purina® Pro Plan® Savor Shredded Blend Adult Dog Food - Chicken & Rice
          p
          b DESCRIPTION:
          p Your dog will love this savory mixture of crunchy kibble and tender shredded morsels of real meat with other high-quality ingredients. This textured blend contains approximately 85% hard kibble and 15% shredded pieces, with real chicken, beef or lamb as the number one ingredient. 100% complete and balanced nutrition for adult dogs. 
     
          td    
          tr

      section
        table.table#notesTable
          tr
            img(src='/costume.png' style='width:25%' onclick='onClick(this)' alt='DC Comics™ Superman Pet Costume')
            button.btn(type="button" v-on:click="addNote" style='background-color:orange') BUY
            tr  ₱ 2460.90
          p
            | DC Comics™ Superman Pet Costume
          p
          b DESCRIPTION:
          p It's a bird, it's a plane, it's SUPER DOG! Turn your pooch into the superhero he is with this DC Comics Originals Superman Costume. Lightweight and comfortable, this costume also comes with an attached cape! Your dog will be the hit of the costume parade dressed up as the Pup of Steel. Only at nUB. 
     
          td  
          tr
          tr
          p
            |
            
      section
        table.table#notesTable
          tr
            img(src='/bag-icon.png' style='width:8%' onclick='onClick(this)')
            h1  Shopping Bag 
      
  
      td
      td
        
      section
        table.table#notesTable
          tr
            th Item
            th Description
            th Quantity
            th Price
            
          tr(v-for="note in notes")
            td {{ note.title }}
            td {{ note.description }}
            td
              button.btn(type="button" v-on:click="addNote" style='background-color:orange') Add
              button.btn(v-on:click="deleteNote(note)" style='background-color:grey') Delete
            td
              
          
